!
!	V03-004	JWT0085		Jim Teague	11-Jan-1982
!		Use lib$get_ef to set a timer wait for locked 
!		libraries.  Free with lib$free_ef.  Also add
!		new sanity id for compressed libraries.
!
!	V03-003	JWT0067		Jim Teague	11-Nov-1982
!		Enlarged the space allocated for DCX records;
!		made LBR clean up after itself more thoroughly;
!		for library creation, if a related name block is
!		passed, then USE IT.
!
!	V03-002	JWT0062		Jim Teague	26-Oct-1982
!		Made DCX descriptors static as part of CTX block.
!
!	V03-001	JWT0056		Jim Teague	16-Sep-1982
!		Implemented interface to DCX data compression/expansion
!		facility.
!
